06:33.226 --> 06:36.354
Lonnie, Lonnie,
weird and scrawny.

06:36.396 --> 06:38.606
Has bad dreams,
so cries to mommy.

06:38.648 --> 06:40.233
Be careful, Lonnie.

06:40.275 --> 06:41.776
He's gonna get you,
Lonnie. He's gonna get you.

