sommelier, but for cheap wines.

15:28.303 --> 15:30.638
-Yeah.
-Yeah, can I get, um,

15:30.680 --> 15:32.307
two of the voodoo
skeleton thing right here?

15:32.349 --> 15:34.601
Hey, look here, don't be
